title: Happy Birthday Bobby! + Brett Eldredge Performs New Song In Studio + Best Country Songs About Beer
itunes:title: Happy Birthday Bobby! + Brett Eldredge Performs New Song In Studio + Best Country Songs About Beer
description:
It’s Bobby’s 41st birthday...so we celebrate all things Bobby today! Brett Eldredge stops by the studio to perform new music and talk about his “Good Day Movement”. Bobby shares a list of things that happened the year he was born. Eddie somewhat gives a speech in his honor. Plus, Bobby shares a list of the 'Best Country Songs about Beer'!
